'''1863年大西洋飓风季'''共有五个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]曾经[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但考虑到19世纪时包括气象卫星、遥感技术在内的现代观测手段尚未面世，基本上只有那些在海上遇到船只或是吹袭人类聚居地的风暴才有文献记载，所以实际形成的热带气旋可能更多。[[气象学|气象学家]][[克里斯托弗·朗诗|克里斯托弗·朗诗]]（{{lang|en|Christopher W. Landsea}}）估计，1851至1885年间实际形成的风暴数量可能比[[大西洋飓风数据库|大西洋飓风数据库]]的记载要多零到六场。<ref>{{cite book | title = Hurricanes and Typhoons: Past, Present and Future | chapter = The Atlantic hurricane database re-analysis project: Documentation for the 1851–1910 alterations and additions to the HURDAT database | author = Christopher W. Landsea | year = 2004 | publisher = Columbia University Press | location = New York | isbn = 0-231-12388-4 | pages = 177–221}}</ref>全季共形成九个热带气旋并且全部达到热带风暴标准，其中五个成为飓风，但没有[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，即没有任何风暴达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的三级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | work = Hurricane Research Division; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2017-01-18 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161225231517/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-12-25 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] }}</ref>。全年所有气旋中有七个是在气象学家何塞·费尔南德斯-帕塔加斯（{{lang|en|Jose Fernandez-Partagas}}）和亨利·迪亚兹（{{lang|en|Henry Diaz}}）1995年出版的文献中首度记载<ref name="partagas-1">{{cite book | author1 = José Fernández-Partagás | author2 = Henry F. Diaz | title = A Reconstruction of Historical Tropical Cyclone Frequency in the Atlantic from Documentary and other Historical Sources: Year 1870 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1858-1864/1863.pdf | publisher = Climate Diagnostics Center, National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Boulder, Colorado | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100601171254/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1858-1864/1863.pdf | deadurl = no | year = 1995 | accessdate = 2017-01-18 | archivedate = 2010-06-01 }}</ref>，另外第九号热带风暴是2003年首度记载<ref name="meta">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_master.html | archivedate = 2016-11-24 | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161124024737/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_master.html | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-25 | location = Miami, Florida | display-authors = etal | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]的大西洋飓风再分析计划认同上述绝大多数发现，并根据这些发现更新大西洋飓风数据库，但部分数据略有调整。

另据迈克尔·切诺维斯和卡里·莫克2013年发表的文献记载，1863年5月24日有风暴在墨西哥湾成型，之后增强成飓风，并因导致[[阿曼达号巡逻舰|阿曼达号巡逻舰]]搁浅而得名“飓风阿曼达”，但大西洋飓风数据库没有收录。这场飓风导致多艘船只倾覆，[[佛罗里达西北狭长地带|佛罗里达西北狭长地带]]沿海地区受到破坏。气旋于5月28日从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，至今仍是大西洋飓风数据库中自1851年起唯一在五月登陆美国的飓风。气旋在海上和陆地上一共夺走至少110条人命。8月，第三号飓风致使美国“班布里奇号”[[双桅横帆船|双桅横帆船]]在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[哈特拉斯_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈特拉斯]]近海沉没，导致80人溺毙。第七号热带风暴令“{{lang|en|JKL}}号”在[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]][[坦皮科|坦皮科]]附近沉没，造成十人死亡。

