8月8日，“弗朗西斯·卡汀号”（{{lang|en|Francis B. Cutting}}）船只在[[纽芬兰与拉布拉多|纽芬兰]][[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）东南偏南约1010公里海域遇到二级飓风<ref name="partagas-1" /><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>，持续风速估计为每小时165公里。风暴朝东北移动，数小时后强度就回落到一级飓风标准，最终在8月9日后失去踪影。<ref name="HURDAT" />
